5|$|Ben Daniels (born David T Daniels on 10 June 1964) is an English actor. Initially {{a celebrated}} stage actor, Daniels was {{nominated}} for an Olivier Award for Best Supporting Actor for Never the Sinner (1991), the Evening Standard Award for Best Actor for 900 Oneonta (1994), Best Actor in the M.E.N. Theatre Awards for Martin Yesterday (1998), and won the 2001 Olivier Award for Best Supporting Actor for his performance in the <b>Arthur</b> <b>Miller</b> play All My Sons.|$|E
